      • getClosestNumber

        public static int getClosestNumber(int number,
                                   int numberToBe,
                                   boolean higherNumbers)
        Returns the closest number that can be divided by the given number
        Parameters:
        number - Integer Number to check
        numberToBe - Integer Number which the returned number should be divideable by
        higherNumbers - Boolean True returns the higher number of two if they are equal, False returns the lower of two numbers
        Returns:
        Integer Closest number to a number which is dividable by the numberToBe
